    "BioNLP corpora in SpanishThe MultiMedica corpus [27] is a multilingual (Japanese, Arabic and Spanish) collection of scientific and popularization texts from the health domain.",
    "It was prepared to conduct corpus and terminology studies and to develop a term extractor.",
    "Only Part-of-Speech (PoS) information was tagged.",
    "Because of proprietary rights, this resource is not freely available.",
    "The MANTRA corpus [28] is a parallel collection of texts in English, French, German, Spanish and Dutch."
  ]
